        <div purpose="subsection" class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4" purpose="report-note">
            <img alt="A globe with two circles" src="/images/icon-globe-36x36@2x.png">
            <h3>The shift to remote work</h3>
            <p>Remote work increases endpoints outside the office, and security teams have less control over these devices' networks. In 2020 MDMs became an overnight priority for protecting organizations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4" purpose="report-note">
