          <h3>22% say their MDM took over a year to implement</h3>
          <p>The largest segment (22.2%) reported that deploying and implementing their MDM took over a year. However, for 18.7%, it took four weeks or less. For 15.7%, it took one to three months, and for 13.1%, it took three to six months. For 16.2%, it took six to nine months, and for 14.1%, it took nine to twelve months.</p>
